description: City: Lake Worth, FLHot Dogs and Veggie Dogs too good for the lunch line! The school lunch you wish you could have had! No Recess until you finish your lunch!Reminiscent of an old public school bus up north, PS561 is a mobile food truck catering to the hungry citizens of South Florida. Serving 100% all beef hot dogs and veggie dogs with all the toppings, as well as a rotation of tasty side snacks and refreshing cold drinks, this is old school summertime flavor at it’s finest!Browse the website to see where and when you can track down PS561. Find us at the coolest events and locations all over South Florida, or just casually parked on the side of a busy street somewhere. You’ll be glad you did!
name: PS561
